      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HES NO ROMEO NZ (2) added to his strong form when third from this barrier in the same grade last week at Bendigo, beaten 2.5 metres. Drew on the back row and worked but toughed out a win prior. Should get his chance from this draw. SURFINGMAKESCENTS (6) returned from a spell and did well to finish second in a decent line-up, beaten just a head at this venue. Has won second-up before and goes very well at this circuit and distance with three wins and two placings from six attempts including her G3 Ladyship Cup victory at the and of last campaign. OUR LUCIANO (9) boxed on to be beaten only 2.6m when resuming. Draws on the back row but usually performs well when second up. METEOR MOTH (8) faded out of a Mildura Cup heat last start but won twice in a row here prior, one of them from this barrier. Can bounce back.",
